WindnTrees application that implements view for data processing.

1. install db-script in mysql server and make sure the path to "world" database in application.properties is correct and mysql-server driver (mysql-connector-java-5.1.45-bin.jar) is placed within webserver (apache-tomcat) library (lib) folder.


Project Development Environement
WindnTrees Maven Application is developed using netbeans IDE configured with latest jdk (java development kit) and maven repository. 

Deployment:
Host WindnTrees.WAR (Web Archive File) within tomcat webserver and (dbscript.sql) in mysql server.

Running:
On successful hosting project can be opened in a webserver using http://localhost:8000/WindnTrees or http://localhost:8000/WindnTrees/world/country.
